      • process

        public static void process(Stats[] statsArr,
                           int uPerTrial,
                           int lgK,
                           double p,
                           StringBuilder dataStr)
        Process the Stats[] array and place the output row into the dataStr.
        Parameters:
        statsArr - the input Stats array
        uPerTrial - the number of uniques per trial for this trial set.
        lgK - log base 2 of configured nominal entries, or k.
        p - the probability sampling rate. 0 < p ≤ 1.0.
        dataStr - The StringBuilder object that is reused for each row of output
